Class RelationType

    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.clarin.webanno.brat.display.model.RelationType

  • public class RelationType
extends Object
    Type of an arc. Defines properties such as color, possible targets, etc. Example: "arcs":[{"type":"anaphoric","color":"green","arrowHead":"triangle,5","labels":["anaphoric"], "targets":["nam"],"dashArray":""}]....
